title: The Suicide Squad
plot: Supervillains Harley Quinn, Bloodsport, Peacemaker and a collection of nutty cons at Belle Reve prison join the super-secret, super-shady Task Force X as they are dropped off at the remote, enemy-infused island of Corto Maltese.
stars: Margot Robbie, Idris Elba, John Cena, Joel Kinnaman
companies: Atlas Entertainment, DC Comics, DC Entertainment

similars.title: Suicide Squad
similars.plot: A secret government agency recruits some of the most dangerous incarcerated super-villains to form a defensive task force. Their first mission: save the world from the apocalypse.
similars.stars: Will Smith, Jared Leto, Margot Robbie

similars.title: Peacemaker
similars.plot: The origin of the DC superhero so dedicated to world peace that he is prepared to use force of arms to achieve it.
similars.stars: Steve Agee, Danielle Brooks, John Cena

similars.title: Black Widow
similars.plot: A film about Natasha Romanoff in her quests between the films Civil War and Infinity War.
similars.stars: Scarlett Johansson, Florence Pugh, David Harbour

similars.title: The Batman
similars.stars: Robert Pattinson, Colin Farrell, Andy Serkis

similars.title: Guardians of the Galaxy: Inferno
similars.plot: A Guardians of the Galaxy video, the Guardians Inferno, featuring 80s pop star Zardu Hasselfrau.
similars.stars: David Hasselhoff, Chris Pratt, Dave Bautista

similars.title: Samaritan
similars.plot: A young boy learns that a superhero who was thought to have gone missing after an epic battle twenty years ago may in fact still be around.
similars.stars: Sylvester Stallone, Martin Starr, Pilou Asbæk

similars.title: Jungle Cruise
similars.plot: Based on Disneyland's theme park ride where a small riverboat takes a group of travelers through a jungle filled with dangerous animals and reptiles but with a supernatural element.
similars.stars: Dwayne Johnson, Emily Blunt, Edgar Ramírez

similars.title: Venom: Let There Be Carnage
similars.plot: Plot unknown. Sequel to the 2018 film 'Venom'.
similars.stars: Tom Hardy, Michelle Williams, Woody Harrelson

similars.title: Birds of Prey
similars.plot: After splitting with the Joker, Harley Quinn joins superheroes Black Canary, Huntress and Renee Montoya to save a young girl from an evil crime lord.
similars.stars: Margot Robbie, Rosie Perez, Mary Elizabeth Winstead

similars.title: Spiral
similars.plot: A criminal mastermind unleashes a twisted form of justice in Spiral, the terrifying new chapter from the book of Saw.
similars.stars: Chris Rock, Samuel L. Jackson, Max Minghella

similars.title: Morbius
similars.plot: Biochemist Michael Morbius tries to cure himself of a rare blood disease, but he inadvertently infects himself with a form of vampirism instead.
similars.stars: Archie Renaux, Jared Leto, Michael Keaton

similars.title: Suicide Squad: Hell to Pay
similars.plot: Task Force X targets a powerful mystical object that they will risk their lives to steal.
similars.stars: Christian Slater, Vanessa Williams, Billy Brown
